  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fight plastic pollution in the bay of Cartagena</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empower communities in the island Tierra Bomba and Punta Arena to fight against pollution through correct waste disposal, avoiding it to end up in the sea. Along with the community we designed and implemented a residue management plan, benefited 3500 inhabitants and continue  educating children at school, working with local recyclers, empowering local leaders and environmental groups to take over responsibilities and bringing volunteers to help in educational, cultural or clean up activities.</narrative>
  </description>
